org.mozilla.javascript での Context の使用
 

Context を返す org.mozilla.javascript のメソッド
 Context ContextFactory.enter()
          Same as enter() with the difference that if a new context needs to be created, then this context factory is used to create it instead of the global context factory.
static Context Context.enter()
          Get a context associated with the current thread, creating one if need be.
 Context ContextFactory.enter(Context cx)
          Same as enter(Context) with the difference that if a new context needs to be created, then this context factory is used to create it instead of the global context factory.
static Context Context.enter(Context cx)
          Get a Context associated with the current thread, using the given Context if need be.
static Context Context.getCurrentContext()
          Get the current Context.
